unittitle.value: Records of the Office of the Director of Academic Program Review (Barnett Hamberger)

abstract.label: Abstract
abstract.value: This collection includes materials from the office of Barnett W. Hamberger, Director of Academic Program Review. The Office of Academic Affairs is responsible for new program registration with the New York State Education Department, as well as overseeing the academic affairs and compliance office serving the intercollegiate athletics program.

p.value:
This collection is in
                <extref ns2:href="http://www.nyu.edu/library/bobst/research/arch/hamberger.htm">
                    <archref> off-site storage</archref> </extref>.

Published citations should take the following form: Identification of item, date (if known); Records of the Office of the Director of Academic Program Review (Barnett Hamberger); RG 9.7; box number; folder number; New York University Archives, New York University Libraries.

Mr. Hamberger has been at NYU since 1965 holding a variety of positions including Director of Branch Campus Affairs, Assistant to the Vice President for Academic Planning, Assistant Vice Chancellor for Student Affairs, and as a faculty member.
Please note: the contents of boxes 1, 2, 49, 56, 60, 67, 71, and 80 have been shifted to other boxes in the collection.
